      Help us personalise your experience

      We use cookies to provide the full functionality of this website, customise your experience, perform analytics and offer you personalised advertisements tailored to your interests on our website, apps and newsletters and via social media platforms.

      We use first- and third-party cookies and other technologies. You can change your preferences at any time or disable cookies in Settings at the bottom of each page.View full policy

      Your preferences

        We care about your privacy.

      Below you will obtain all information about the cookies we use. You can activate and/or deactivate them according to your preferences, except for the cookies that are strictly necessary for the operation of this website. Please note that rejecting some cookies may impact your experience on our website. When you click on Confirm my choices, the cookie selection you have made will be saved. If you want to learn more about cookies and why we use them, you can visit our Cookie Policy.

      Manage Consent Preferences

      Necessary

      Always Active

      Functional or strictly necessary cookies ensure that Rituals websites and apps can function correctly. These ensure functionalities such as remembering your credentials for the log-in; the ability to store your products in the shopping; remembering your preferred language, managing your cookies consent choices; detection of security vulnerabilities and others. This also includes some analytical cookies with little privacy impact, such as those used to count visitors.

      Analytical

      These cookies measure how you use our website, such as how you got to the website, the pages you visit, how long you spend on each page, and the clicks made.

      Marketing cookies

      These cookies may be placed across our website by us or by our advertising partners. Data collected from these cookies is used build a profile of your interests and show you relevant advertisements with our services and products on our and third party websites, for example on social media platforms.
